ollapse\">\n                    <ul class=\"nav navbar-nav navbar-right\">\n                        <!-- ADD MENU LINKS HERE. THESE ARE NON-FUNCTIONAL EXAMPLES. -->\n                        <li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\">Our Store</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/usr/dealsonlywebstore\">About Us</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"https://contact.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?ContactUserNextGen&amp;recipient=dealsonlywebstore\">Contact Us</a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div><!--/.nav-collapse -->\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <div>\n                    <div class=\"main-image\">\n                        <img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/72109/hQG0IC7y3OSQ79PabEzLdFZC3aWQjd-metaanVtcF9yb3BlX2RseF9wYXJlbnQuanBn-.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"Responsive image\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <h3>Product Details</h3>\n                <!-- ADD A NEW ROW FOR EACH PRODUCT ATTRIBUTE YOU WANT TO SHOW IN THE TABLE OR YOU CAN REMOVE THE TABLE COMPLETELY-->\n                <div class=\"product-specs\">\n                    <table>\n                        <tbody>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"><br></td><td class=\"attr-right\"><br></td></tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">COMFORTABLE MOLDED PLASTIC HANDLES - Easy for little hands to grip, ensuring hours of hassle-free play.</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">BRIGHT EYE-CATCTHING COLORS - Fun, vibrant design that keeps kids engaged and excited to jump.</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">ULTRA-DURABLE ROPE - Built to last through endless jumping, twirling, and active play.</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">ENCOURAGES ACTIVE LIFESTYLES - Promotes fitness, coordination, and healthy habits in a fun, playful way.</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">KID-FRIENDLY AND SAFE - Perfectly sized and suitable for children ages 3 and up.</td>\n                            </tr>\n                        </tbody>\n                    </table>\n                </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <h1>Officially Licensed Girls Cartoon Deluxe Jump Rope Molded Handles 7 Feet (5 Characters)</h1>\n                <h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">19.99</span></h2>\n                <p data-start=\"127\" data-end=\"256\">Get your little ones moving with our <strong data-start=\"164\" data-end=\"202\">Officially Licensed Kids Jump Rope</strong>&nbsp;- the perfect mix of fun, fitness, and timeless play! Features either Minnie Mouse, Hello Kitty, Stitch, Barbie, or Disney Princess.</p><p>Designed with easy-grip molded plastic handles, this jump rope is made for little hands to hold comfortably, so the fun never skips a beat. Its bright, vibrant colors make every jump more exciting and visually engaging, capturing kids' attention the moment they pick it up.</p><p>Crafted from a super durable rope, it's built to withstand countless hours of jumping, twirling, and high-energy play. This classic toy isn’t just about fun - it promotes physical activity, coordination, and a healthy, active lifestyle in a way that feels like pure play.</p><p>Perfect for ages 3 and up, it’s safe, simple, and endlessly entertaining—whether in the backyard, at recess, or as the perfect birthday gift. Let them jump, laugh, and grow strong - one skip at a time!</p>\n                <div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n                    <div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-100\">\n                        <p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n                        <p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n                        <a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n                <p>© 2025</p>\n            </div> <!-- /footer -->\n    \n        </div> <!-- /container -->\n        <div style=\"clear:both\"><br><table></table>\n        </div>\n",
